125
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,280
Just as a favor.

126
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,680
Alright, alright, fine! I'll help.

127
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,280
I'll send you their resumes later.

128
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,040
Okay.

129
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,319
Send them over,

130
