173
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:34,440
The rest

174
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,279
is up to you.

175
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,639
Thank you, Director Xu.

176
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,960
I really appreciate it.

177
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,720
Thank you for everything you've done for Xinmiao.

178
