253
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,720
is feeling uneasy.

254
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,200
I don't really have the standing

255
00:11:57,399 --> 00:11:58,560
to console everyone.

256
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:00,519
But today,

257
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:02,320
