885
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:38,560
Are you sure?

886
00:39:39,080 --> 00:39:39,839
Yeah.

887
00:39:39,839 --> 00:39:40,560
Then why didn't you discuss

888
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,799
your unemployment with me?

889
00:39:43,839 --> 00:39:44,480
If I hadn't gone

890
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:45,440
to your company today,

891
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:45,799
I wouldn't have known

892
00:39:45,799 --> 00:39:47,239
what you've been up to recently.

893
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,400
Let's keep things separate.

894
00:39:49,799 --> 00:39:51,080
Now let's focus on your issue.

895
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,359
Don't think you can hide your secrets.

896
00:39:54,359 --> 00:39:55,359
I know why you went to Beijing.

897
00:39:55,359 --> 00:39:56,600
I know who you met.

898
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:57,600
Mei Yiduo, right?

899
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:58,759
For what reason you met with her?

900
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:00,040
To help you find a job?

901
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:00,960
Did she help?

902
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:04,639
Someone knocks the door.

903
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:05,960
You don't need to hide.

904
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,040
This day was bound to come.

905
00:40:08,639 --> 00:40:09,279
Hey!

906
00:40:09,279 --> 00:40:10,520
Hello, Uncle.

907
00:40:10,520 --> 00:40:10,759
Hi, Brother-in-law.

908
00:40:10,759 --> 00:40:11,199
Where's Haowen?

909
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:11,960
He is coming.

910
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:12,759
Sis.

911
00:40:13,159 --> 00:40:13,679
Come in.

912
00:40:13,799 --> 00:40:14,359
Come in.

913
00:40:14,359 --> 00:40:15,319
What brings you here?

914
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:16,839
Sis.

915
00:40:16,839 --> 00:40:17,679
We brought some seafood.

916
00:40:17,799 --> 00:40:18,920
Mom and Dad said it's really delicious.

917
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:19,960
We brought some for you

918
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:20,480
Great, great!

919
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,199
Come on in.

920
00:40:21,199 --> 00:40:21,600
Sure thing.

921
00:40:22,639 --> 00:40:23,880
I didn't change my shoes.

922
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:25,639
Let your brother-in-law to bother anyway.

923
00:40:25,679 --> 00:40:26,960
He's taken to cleaning lately.

924
00:40:27,400 --> 00:40:28,279
Really?

925
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,880
Look at this place.

926
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,759
It's cluttered everywhere.

927
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,400
Isn't it cramped with you all living here?

928
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,120
You've only just been in a big house.

929
00:40:36,359 --> 00:40:37,639
Complaining about everything...

930
00:40:37,759 --> 00:40:39,239
Why don't you move to Mom's place for now?

931
00:40:39,239 --> 00:40:40,359
At least it's more spacious there.

932
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:42,839
When will you move into the new house?

933
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,600
Maybe in a year.

934
00:40:44,839 --> 00:40:46,359
There's still renovation to be done.

935
00:40:47,239 --> 00:40:48,199
How much did you loan?

936
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,960
I heard from Mom that

937
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,560
you have to pay back a lot each month.

938
00:40:52,639 --> 00:40:54,400
Who buys a house without a mortgage?

939
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:56,359
But with all your overtime,

940
00:40:56,359 --> 00:40:57,759
it's all going to the bank's interest.

941
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:58,639
That's not ideal.

942
00:40:58,799 --> 00:40:59,639
You should borrow some from Haowen for now.

943
00:40:59,639 --> 00:41:00,199
Haowen.

944
00:41:00,679 --> 00:41:01,239
Haowen, come here.

945
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:01,920
Come.

946
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:03,679
What's up?

947
00:41:03,759 --> 00:41:03,960
Nothing.

948
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:04,520
My sis...

949
00:41:07,799 --> 00:41:08,480
Nothing?

950
00:41:09,839 --> 00:41:10,239
Sis.

951
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,960
I...

952
00:41:12,279 --> 00:41:13,600
I'll make you some seafood.

953
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,400
I'll show you my skills.

954
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,520
It's really good.

955
00:41:15,759 --> 00:41:16,880
Didn't you just eat?

956
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,639
Still hungry?

957
00:41:18,799 --> 00:41:20,600
I just didn't want to eat too much

958
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:22,000
at Mom and Dad's home.

959
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,400
Right.

960
00:41:22,839 --> 00:41:23,520
You are hungry.

961
00:41:23,799 --> 00:41:24,440
Have some more.

962
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:26,239
Go wash the seafood.

963
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:27,560
I don't know how.

964
00:41:29,639 --> 00:41:30,960
You don't know how to wash seafood?

965
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:32,000
No, I don't.

966
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,159
Come on.

967
00:41:33,319 --> 00:41:34,560
What?

968
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,120
I'll show you.

969
00:41:38,679 --> 00:41:40,040
I'm doing this for your own good.

970
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,480
Why aren't you appreciative?

971
00:41:41,839 --> 00:41:42,839
I'll cover the renovation costs.

972
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:43,319
No need.

973
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:44,480
Even though we're not

974
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,560
as wealthy as you,

975
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:46,880
we're not short on money.

976
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:48,520
Not lacking...

977
00:41:49,319 --> 00:41:50,400
With two executives in the house,

978
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,639
you're not short on money.

979
00:41:51,639 --> 00:41:52,560
Right, Brother-in-law?

980
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:53,960
Yes!

981
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:02,719
Sis.

982
00:42:03,719 --> 00:42:05,359
You seem stressed lately.

983
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,480
Your complexion doesn't look good.

984
00:42:07,639 --> 00:42:08,560
You seem a bit down.

985
00:42:09,239 --> 00:42:10,239
A little bit upset.

986
00:42:10,639 --> 00:42:12,000
Are you going through menopause?

987
00:42:12,080 --> 00:42:13,799
You've mastered the art of conversation.

988
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,440
I just...

989
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,120
I went to the gynecology department

990
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:16,480
at the provincial hospital yesterday.

991
00:42:16,639 --> 00:42:17,560
I saw a woman

992
00:42:17,560 --> 00:42:18,359
who was only thirty-four

993
00:42:18,359 --> 00:42:19,199
and she's already gone through menopause.

994
00:42:19,279 --> 00:42:20,319
Did she tell you that?

995
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:23,080
Just keep an eye on it.

996
00:42:23,799 --> 00:42:24,839
We women need to take care of ourselves.

997
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:26,480
Here's a beauty salon card for you.

998
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:26,960
No need.

999
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:28,080
I don't have time to use it.

1000
00:42:28,319 --> 00:42:29,319
Just take it.

1001
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:30,639
I'm pregnant now.

1002
00:42:30,839 --> 00:42:31,639
I won't be using it.

1003
00:42:31,839 --> 00:42:32,359
Okay, okay.

1004
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:33,639
Anything else you can't use?

1005
00:42:33,639 --> 00:42:34,799
You can all give them to me.

1006
00:42:36,679 --> 00:42:37,480
Sis.

1007
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,199
Is there anything wrong?

1008
00:42:40,199 --> 00:42:42,440
You are weird today.

1009
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,960
You found out?

1010
00:42:50,759 --> 00:42:51,440
Brother-in-law.

1011
00:42:51,799 --> 00:42:53,359
I'll add more of this ginger paste.

1012
00:42:53,359 --> 00:42:54,239
Garlic paste, okay?

1013
00:42:54,239 --> 00:42:55,880
Later, I'll pour hot oil over it.

1014
00:42:56,839 --> 00:42:58,719
This seafood, fresh seafood,

1015
00:42:58,719 --> 00:43:00,040
shouldn't have any chili.

1016
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:01,480
Or peppercorns.

1017
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:02,839
It should be authentic.

1018
00:43:03,199 --> 00:43:04,120
Just like this.

1019
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:10,359
Brother-in-law.

1020
00:43:11,520 --> 00:43:13,639
Why did you

1021
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:15,040
invite us today?

1022
00:43:16,359 --> 00:43:17,880
Just to get together.

1023
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:20,520
Meng'an said she missed you.

1024
00:43:21,839 --> 00:43:23,279
Me? No way.

1025
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:24,639
She missed her sister.

1026
00:43:25,839 --> 00:43:27,000
I missed you, okay?

1027
00:43:28,239 --> 00:43:28,880
Okay.

1028
00:43:29,120 --> 00:43:29,839
I'll make sure this seafood

1029
00:43:29,839 --> 00:43:30,839
turns out perfectly.

1030
00:43:30,839 --> 00:43:31,719
It'll be delicious.

1031
00:43:35,839 --> 00:43:37,080
Did you bring the wine?

1032
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:37,799
Sure.

1033
00:43:38,799 --> 00:43:39,159
Good.

